WEBVTT

00:01:59.420 --> 00:01:59.980
Qi Xiaowei

00:02:00.000 --> 00:02:01.280
That painting isn't me at all.

00:02:01.840 --> 00:02:02.879
Who did you paint?

00:02:03.680 --> 00:02:04.719
Behind Xiaofang's back,

00:02:04.879 --> 00:02:05.700
Is there someone else?

00:02:06.280 --> 00:02:06.900
Don't talk nonsense.

00:02:07.560 --> 00:02:08.219
What's going on?

00:02:09.979 --> 00:02:11.319
Xiaowei, what's this about?

00:02:13.300 --> 00:02:13.560
Sis.

00:02:15.900 --> 00:02:16.360
He...

00:02:17.379 --> 00:02:18.900
Was born in 1841,

00:02:19.039 --> 00:02:20.460
Died in 1919,

00:02:20.560 --> 00:02:22.000
A major painter of Impressionism,

00:02:22.300 --> 00:02:23.580
Born in Limoges, France.

00:02:23.800 --> 00:02:24.379
His full name is

00:02:24.500 --> 00:02:27.080
Pierre-Auguste Renoir.

00:02:27.300 --> 00:02:28.400
Hurry up. Give it to us straight.

00:02:29.199 --> 00:02:30.699
This painting was done by

00:02:30.800 --> 00:02:31.800
The French artist, Mr. Renoir.

00:02:32.120 --> 00:02:33.919
Not by Mr. Qi here.

00:02:34.439 --> 00:02:35.919
Look, look, he just copied it.

00:02:35.919 --> 00:02:37.000
That's not our Xiaofang.

00:02:37.099 --> 00:02:37.979
Come, show everybody.

00:02:37.979 --> 00:02:38.520
Come on, come on.

00:02:38.639 --> 00:02:39.340
Show everyone.

00:02:39.680 --> 00:02:40.639
You just copied this.

00:02:40.639 --> 00:02:42.000
Why did you insist it was me?

00:02:42.000 --> 00:02:42.659
It's exactly the same.

00:02:42.680 --> 00:02:43.460
Copied straight from it.

00:02:43.719 --> 00:02:45.439
I never told anyone that.

00:02:45.560 --> 00:02:46.520
But you never stepped up

00:02:46.539 --> 00:02:47.879
To clear our Xiaofang's name.

00:02:47.939 --> 00:02:49.219
Are you really that stupid, kid?

00:02:49.520 --> 00:02:50.659
You didn't paint her.

00:02:50.659 --> 00:02:52.659
Why wouldn't you just admit it?

00:02:53.259 --> 00:02:55.240
You addicted to being talked about behind your back?

00:02:57.379 --> 00:02:58.360
Last night you said

00:02:58.740 --> 00:03:00.439
You painted me from your heart.

00:03:01.620 --> 00:03:02.520
That was a lie too.

00:03:02.560 --> 00:03:03.379
He didn't just lie to you.

00:03:03.400 --> 00:03:04.479
He lied to everyone.

00:03:04.639 --> 00:03:05.919
Isn't this just building up a persona?

00:03:05.919 --> 00:03:06.680
An artist.

00:03:06.919 --> 00:03:08.099
A real artist creates original work.

00:03:08.159 --> 00:03:09.479
Copying doesn't make you an artist.

00:03:09.800 --> 00:03:11.139
Calling himself an artist,

00:03:11.379 --> 00:03:12.740
Just to trick our Xiaofang

00:03:12.879 --> 00:03:13.780
And win her over.

00:03:14.240 --> 00:03:15.979
You wanted everyone to misunderstand,

00:03:16.300 --> 00:03:17.479
To show off your skills, right?

00:03:17.580 --> 00:03:18.360
That's enough, Fanmei.

00:03:18.360 --> 00:03:19.219
Fantastic.

00:03:19.340 --> 00:03:21.000
Now the truth is out, isn't it?

00:03:21.539 --> 00:03:22.379
The one who's disgraced now

00:03:22.379 --> 00:03:23.340
Isn't our Xiaofang.

00:03:23.479 --> 00:03:25.479
It's this fake painter, Qi Xiaowei!

00:03:25.560 --> 00:03:26.139
Yeah, fake painter!

00:03:26.139 --> 00:03:27.219
Alright, alright, what's with you all?

00:03:30.379 --> 00:03:31.819
Did I make you nervous?

00:03:35.340 --> 00:03:36.319
Anyone can paint that.

00:03:38.439 --> 00:03:39.400
Anyone can paint that.

00:03:40.319 --> 00:03:41.400
If she hadn't been

00:03:41.479 --> 00:03:42.900
Kissing me and doing whatever that day,

00:03:42.900 --> 00:03:43.900
I could've painted it myself.

00:03:44.020 --> 00:03:44.879
Oh, is that so?

00:03:45.840 --> 00:03:47.580
Didn't I tell you to stay home?

00:03:47.759 --> 00:03:49.580
Who knew this kid would be such a jerk?

00:03:50.120 --> 00:03:50.719
What are you doing?

00:03:50.819 --> 00:03:51.699
Don't hold me back!

00:03:51.819 --> 00:03:52.979
I'm gonna teach him a lesson!

00:05:01.519 --> 00:05:02.560
Master of Nudes

00:05:04.180 --> 00:05:04.800
He's not the shameful one.

00:05:04.800 --> 00:05:05.639
His wife is the shameful one.

00:05:05.639 --> 00:05:06.240
He's even more shameful.

00:05:06.300 --> 00:05:07.300
He can't paint at all.

00:05:07.600 --> 00:05:08.660
A fake art master.

00:05:08.800 --> 00:05:09.600
It's all plagiarism.

00:05:10.120 --> 00:05:10.879
Isn't it?

00:05:11.220 --> 00:05:12.860
They said it's art.

00:05:27.060 --> 00:05:27.860
About Xiaofang and

00:05:28.819 --> 00:05:30.240
Xiaowei's marriage,

00:05:31.300 --> 00:05:32.920
Everyone's watching.

00:05:35.579 --> 00:05:36.879
They're all waiting for the drama.

00:05:37.759 --> 00:05:38.660
You parents

00:05:39.040 --> 00:05:40.079
Not only fail to settle things,

00:05:40.819 --> 00:05:42.500
You're making the conflict worse.

00:05:44.120 --> 00:05:45.800
Afraid folks won't have a show to watch?

00:05:46.160 --> 00:05:47.899
Are you planning to sell tickets too?

00:05:47.980 --> 00:05:48.980
Isn't it the Qi family

00:05:48.980 --> 00:05:50.139
Who set up this whole stage?

00:05:50.240 --> 00:05:51.360
They dragged us up onto it.

00:05:51.639 --> 00:05:52.240
So we've got no choice

00:05:52.319 --> 00:05:53.160
But to play along till the end.

00:05:53.379 --> 00:05:54.220
Set up the stage?

00:05:54.800 --> 00:05:56.560
You're the ones who love the drama most.

00:05:58.120 --> 00:05:58.779
Look at yourselves.

00:05:59.180 --> 00:06:00.199
For the sake of the two kids,

00:06:00.740 --> 00:06:01.740
Each side should give a little.

00:06:02.579 --> 00:06:04.720
Or are you going to keep performing

00:06:04.860 --> 00:06:05.800
On this stage?

00:06:06.139 --> 00:06:07.439
Until you sing their marriage

00:06:07.480 --> 00:06:08.259
Right into the ground?

00:06:10.740 --> 00:06:12.259
Even if you two can't become in-laws,

00:06:12.740 --> 00:06:14.319
Don't ruin things for the kids.

00:06:15.620 --> 00:06:16.160
Now,

00:06:16.740 --> 00:06:17.600
The truth's out in the open.

00:06:18.279 --> 00:06:18.779
The painting,

00:06:19.439 --> 00:06:20.740
His family didn't paint it.

00:06:21.060 --> 00:06:23.100
And her family didn't strip for it.

00:06:23.879 --> 00:06:25.660
So what's still the problem?

00:06:25.879 --> 00:06:27.060
Their marriage

00:06:27.339 --> 00:06:29.660
Is only being blocked by you parents.

00:06:30.279 --> 00:06:30.819
Qi Deyao,

00:06:31.399 --> 00:06:32.100
Let me ask you again.

00:06:32.939 --> 00:06:34.540
Is Xiaowei getting married or not?

00:06:35.540 --> 00:06:36.379
I never said he wasn't.

00:06:37.319 --> 00:06:37.819
Fanyan,

00:06:38.079 --> 00:06:38.779
I'll ask you too.

00:06:39.139 --> 00:06:40.319
Is Xiaofang getting married or not?

00:06:40.680 --> 00:06:41.879
I never said she wasn't.

00:06:42.000 --> 00:06:43.360
So what's the hold-up?

00:06:44.180 --> 00:06:44.879
Attitude, and the bride price.

00:06:47.920 --> 00:06:49.660
On the bride price issue,

00:06:49.800 --> 00:06:50.939
We weren't going to nitpick.

00:06:52.180 --> 00:06:52.779
But,

00:06:53.100 --> 00:06:55.279
He took advantage of Xiaofang being pregnant,

00:06:55.339 --> 00:06:57.019
And won't show any goodwill.

00:06:57.060 --> 00:06:58.439
Ever since he was young,

00:06:58.500 --> 00:07:00.139
He's been slicker than a monkey with a tail.

00:07:00.319 --> 00:07:01.519
A total cheapskate,

00:07:01.560 --> 00:07:02.500
Through and through.

00:07:02.579 --> 00:07:03.680
Won't part with a single penny.

00:07:04.100 --> 00:07:05.600
Yet he wants a grandson for free,

00:07:05.720 --> 00:07:06.720
And a daughter-in-law for free.

00:07:06.939 --> 00:07:07.879
Where on earth do you find

00:07:08.060 --> 00:07:09.139
Pies falling from the sky,

00:07:09.319 --> 00:07:10.920
With vinegar and garlic on the side,

00:07:11.000 --> 00:07:11.819
All served up for you?

00:07:11.899 --> 00:07:12.600
In your dreams!

00:07:13.399 --> 00:07:14.420
Yang Fanyan,

00:07:14.819 --> 00:07:16.600
Quit acting so high and mighty.

00:07:18.160 --> 00:07:19.600
Talking like you're on a storytelling stage.

00:07:20.279 --> 00:07:21.660
You're only doing this

00:07:21.800 --> 00:07:22.839
To sound self-righteous.

00:07:23.379 --> 00:07:24.560
Fine, let's just drag this out.

00:07:24.740 --> 00:07:25.519
I can wait it out.

00:07:25.660 --> 00:07:27.180
But Xiaofang's belly can't wait.

00:07:27.660 --> 00:07:28.860
That's a low blow.

00:07:29.040 --> 00:07:29.660
Absolutely nasty.

00:07:29.720 --> 00:07:30.660
You're the nasty one!

00:07:30.779 --> 00:07:32.199
You don't care about Xiaofang's feelings.

00:07:32.319 --> 00:07:33.319
How can anyone be so heartless?

00:07:33.319 --> 00:07:33.819
You're the selfish one!

00:07:34.000 --> 00:07:35.480
All right, all right, enough!

00:07:35.480 --> 00:07:36.300
How can you be so mean?

00:07:36.560 --> 00:07:38.100
I'm warning both of you.

00:07:38.240 --> 00:07:39.600
The higher-ups are cracking down

00:07:39.899 --> 00:07:41.279
On rural marriage customs.

00:07:42.160 --> 00:07:43.500
I'll give you three days.

00:07:43.879 --> 00:07:44.660
You'd better work it out.

00:07:44.800 --> 00:07:45.319
Our village

00:07:45.399 --> 00:07:46.839
Can't become a bad example.

00:07:47.000 --> 00:07:48.339
Or get reported by another village.

00:07:49.720 --> 00:07:50.740
Report it if they want.

00:07:54.500 --> 00:07:56.220
I'll help them report her.

00:08:05.959 --> 00:08:06.920
Made up your minds, then?

00:08:07.879 --> 00:08:08.779
Then let's get started.

00:08:25.319 --> 00:08:25.759
This...

00:08:33.240 --> 00:08:34.500
Why is there such a big gap?

00:08:35.779 --> 00:08:37.620
You two sisters live in the big city,

00:08:37.899 --> 00:08:38.639
You've seen the world,

00:08:38.860 --> 00:08:39.600
You have high standards.

00:08:40.919 --> 00:08:43.320
But Xiaowei and Xiaofang,

00:08:43.879 --> 00:08:45.139
They're village folks after all.

00:08:45.440 --> 00:08:46.519
Let's be realistic.

00:08:46.840 --> 00:08:47.600
Around here,

00:08:47.600 --> 00:08:49.980
I've never heard of anything that high.

00:08:51.080 --> 00:08:52.480
You old country bumpkin!

00:08:52.759 --> 00:08:53.940
Just talk business.

00:08:54.179 --> 00:08:55.279
That smirk is disgusting.

00:08:55.620 --> 00:08:56.039
I...

00:08:56.240 --> 00:08:56.820
Yang Fanmei!

00:08:57.500 --> 00:08:58.720
Why do you insult me the moment you open your mouth?

00:08:58.840 --> 00:08:59.860
Do you have a heart?

00:08:59.960 --> 00:09:01.480
If you did, would you offer so little?

00:09:02.460 --> 00:09:02.779
Hey now,

00:09:05.080 --> 00:09:06.120
This is a harmonious society.

00:09:07.200 --> 00:09:08.820
Are your two families becoming in-laws,

00:09:08.899 --> 00:09:09.919
Or enemies?

00:09:10.559 --> 00:09:11.539
As for the bride price,

00:09:11.779 --> 00:09:12.740
How much you give,

00:09:13.139 --> 00:09:14.659
It's really just a matter of dignity, isn't it?

00:09:15.679 --> 00:09:16.580
Exactly.

00:09:16.779 --> 00:09:18.879
Who doesn't want to save face?

00:09:20.539 --> 00:09:21.340
Well said.

00:09:26.480 --> 00:09:27.279
Old Qi,

00:09:28.120 --> 00:09:29.779
I'll put it all on the line.

00:09:31.039 --> 00:09:31.799
I'll sell

00:09:32.399 --> 00:09:34.820
My gold dowry bracelet.

00:09:35.480 --> 00:09:36.980
Let's put together for Xiaofang

00:09:37.460 --> 00:09:38.080
Fifty-eight thousand,

00:09:38.639 --> 00:09:40.659
Eight hundred and eighty-eight.

00:09:41.779 --> 00:09:42.539
Qiu Mei,

00:09:43.559 --> 00:09:44.519
I'm sorry to put you through this.

00:09:45.159 --> 00:09:46.659
Never mind me,

00:09:47.039 --> 00:09:48.919
Just don't let Xiaofang down, right?

00:09:49.000 --> 00:09:50.320
And this ring of mine, throw it in too.

00:09:50.320 --> 00:09:51.080
Qi Deyao,

00:09:51.080 --> 00:09:51.580
Is that enough?

00:09:53.100 --> 00:09:54.159
There are no cameras here,

00:09:55.159 --> 00:09:56.139
This isn't a livestream.

00:09:56.419 --> 00:09:57.320
Cut the act.

00:09:58.200 --> 00:09:59.559
That new car of yours,

00:09:59.980 --> 00:10:00.779
At the very least,

00:10:01.139 --> 00:10:02.440
Cost 150,000.

00:10:03.039 --> 00:10:04.779
I hear come spring, your little house

00:10:04.779 --> 00:10:06.139
Is getting three more floors added.

00:10:07.500 --> 00:10:08.940
That's got to be over 100,000, right?

00:10:09.379 --> 00:10:09.779
That's right.

00:10:10.220 --> 00:10:11.539
Aren't you planning to lease

00:10:11.559 --> 00:10:12.460
The whole eastern hilltop?

00:10:13.080 --> 00:10:14.379
That land is at least thirty mu.

00:10:14.759 --> 00:10:15.820
100,000 a year.

00:10:16.220 --> 00:10:17.539
If you lease for more years,

00:10:17.639 --> 00:10:18.240
There's even a discount.

00:10:18.620 --> 00:10:18.980
Right?

00:10:19.919 --> 00:10:20.500
Old Qi,

00:10:21.200 --> 00:10:22.639
You don't look short on cash.

00:10:23.259 --> 00:10:23.919
Deng Erjin,

00:10:24.820 --> 00:10:25.779
Whose side are you on?

00:10:26.379 --> 00:10:27.539
It's all just rumors, Qi Deyao.

00:10:28.100 --> 00:10:29.600
You're being too calculating.

00:10:30.159 --> 00:10:31.399
But you can can't just treat everyone else

00:10:31.740 --> 00:10:32.960
Like they're idiots.

00:10:34.080 --> 00:10:34.620
You...

00:10:35.539 --> 00:10:36.679
Think it over again.

00:10:39.980 --> 00:10:40.419
Sis,

00:10:41.200 --> 00:10:42.059
Did you hear?

00:10:43.360 --> 00:10:45.399
A family in the next village couldn't agree,

00:10:45.519 --> 00:10:46.419
The bride backed out.

00:10:46.480 --> 00:10:47.779
They'd already had their wedding night,

00:10:48.340 --> 00:10:49.940
And it fell apart right on the spot.

00:10:50.240 --> 00:10:51.600
She's even suing the guy.

00:10:51.919 --> 00:10:52.460
Yes, yes, yes.

00:10:52.639 --> 00:10:53.580
On WeChat,

00:10:53.720 --> 00:10:55.039
It's gone viral already.

00:10:56.259 --> 00:10:57.320
I heard in the end, the guy

00:10:57.460 --> 00:10:58.639
Didn't even get the baby.

00:10:59.600 --> 00:11:01.340
Making stuff up, who are you trying to scare?

00:11:01.539 --> 00:11:02.700
Being all snide, honestly.

00:11:02.700 --> 00:11:03.320
Qi Deyao,

00:11:03.779 --> 00:11:04.919
Even for a legal married couple,

00:11:05.039 --> 00:11:06.279
If the wife doesn't consent

00:11:06.419 --> 00:11:07.860
And the husband forces sex,

00:11:08.000 --> 00:11:09.519
He still bears legal responsibility.

00:11:10.259 --> 00:11:11.360
I've heard about this.

00:11:11.820 --> 00:11:12.639
That guy apparently...

00:11:13.000 --> 00:11:13.659
I'm not deaf.

00:11:19.659 --> 00:11:20.159
Old Qi.

00:11:21.059 --> 00:11:21.679
Old Qi.

00:11:22.139 --> 00:11:23.019
Don't get worked up.

00:11:23.299 --> 00:11:24.340
There are still two days left.

00:11:56.299 --> 00:11:56.820
Xiaofang,

00:12:01.559 --> 00:12:03.820
I've cleared everything up.

00:12:05.179 --> 00:12:07.980
It was Xiaozhang who stupidly sent it out.

00:12:10.019 --> 00:12:11.139
I've already cut ties with him.

00:12:15.320 --> 00:12:16.779
I never told anyone else

00:12:17.539 --> 00:12:19.059
That the painting was of you.

00:12:20.320 --> 00:12:21.860
I don't know how it just...

00:12:21.919 --> 00:12:23.179
Got spread around like this.

00:12:26.919 --> 00:12:27.539
And then

00:12:29.600 --> 00:12:30.820
That day, with so many people

00:12:30.820 --> 00:12:31.799
Talking about me like that,

00:12:34.240 --> 00:12:35.379
I just couldn't

00:12:35.440 --> 00:12:36.620
Control my emotions

00:12:37.379 --> 00:12:38.179
And I blurted your name out.

00:12:40.500 --> 00:12:41.139
I'm sorry.

00:12:44.879 --> 00:12:46.039
That's not what I wanted to ask.

00:12:48.779 --> 00:12:50.159
Then why did you call me over?

00:12:53.860 --> 00:12:54.480
No, well...

00:12:55.039 --> 00:12:56.500
There are people around here.

00:12:57.840 --> 00:12:58.879
What are you thinking?

00:13:00.700 --> 00:13:02.360
You didn't finish painting me last time, right?

00:13:03.399 --> 00:13:04.440
Just paint me again.

00:13:06.100 --> 00:13:07.559
This time I'm not taking my clothes off.

00:13:07.580 --> 00:13:08.320
And I'm not kissing you.

00:13:09.940 --> 00:13:10.940
Xiaochao told me

00:13:11.179 --> 00:13:13.139
She took artistic photos before giving birth.

00:13:13.759 --> 00:13:14.759
I want a keepsake too.

00:13:15.559 --> 00:13:16.100
But I thought

00:13:16.220 --> 00:13:18.000
Having you paint me would mean more.

00:13:20.419 --> 00:13:21.179
Right now?

00:13:44.360 --> 00:13:46.100
How can you paint if you don't look at me?

00:13:51.299 --> 00:13:52.500
Let's do it another day.

00:13:53.179 --> 00:13:54.080
This is too sudden.

00:13:56.559 --> 00:13:57.440
Another day.

00:13:59.860 --> 00:14:01.159
When exactly is "another day"?

00:14:07.519 --> 00:14:08.820
I didn't do anything this time.

00:14:08.899 --> 00:14:10.159
And you still can't paint?

00:14:11.820 --> 00:14:12.419
Xiaowei.

00:14:12.919 --> 00:14:14.059
It's just the two of us now.

00:14:14.100 --> 00:14:14.919
Is there something

00:14:14.940 --> 00:14:16.059
You need to tell me?

00:14:29.879 --> 00:14:31.740
So when you agreed to paint me last time,

00:14:32.980 --> 00:14:34.120
You were actually lying?

00:14:34.940 --> 00:14:35.679
I wasn't lying.

00:14:36.200 --> 00:14:37.779
I really did want to paint you.

00:14:38.019 --> 00:14:39.220
When rumors about that painting spread,

00:14:39.220 --> 00:14:40.120
Why didn't you speak up

00:14:40.120 --> 00:14:40.919
And say something?

00:14:51.039 --> 00:14:51.720
I can't paint.

00:14:54.259 --> 00:14:55.480
I can only copy.

00:14:57.700 --> 00:14:58.940
I'm not an artist.

00:14:59.679 --> 00:15:01.019
That studio of mine,

00:15:01.299 --> 00:15:01.940
It's just

00:15:02.419 --> 00:15:04.440
A studio that copies famous paintings.

00:15:06.279 --> 00:15:07.360
I'm just an apprentice.

00:15:08.179 --> 00:15:09.419
Not any kind of artist.

00:15:11.740 --> 00:15:12.720
I'm sorry, Xiaofang.

00:15:13.019 --> 00:15:15.139
I just wanted you to think highly of me.

00:15:17.120 --> 00:15:18.279
I like you.

00:15:18.340 --> 00:15:19.440
Whether you're an artist

00:15:19.539 --> 00:15:21.279
Or can paint doesn't matter.

00:15:22.360 --> 00:15:23.840
But you shouldn't have lied to me.

00:15:25.120 --> 00:15:25.840
I'm sorry, okay?

00:15:26.940 --> 00:15:27.559
I just...

00:15:28.340 --> 00:15:29.980
I only lied to you about this one thing.

00:15:32.100 --> 00:15:33.100
Nothing else.

00:15:35.299 --> 00:15:36.100
Please forgive me.

00:15:45.360 --> 00:15:46.000
Qi Xiaowei.

00:15:47.179 --> 00:15:49.100
I cherish what we have,

00:15:52.059 --> 00:15:53.620
So I'll trust you one more time.

00:16:03.000 --> 00:16:03.860
I'm sorry, okay?

00:16:07.679 --> 00:16:08.919
This time my aunts

00:16:09.000 --> 00:16:09.919
Are really furious.

00:16:10.080 --> 00:16:11.039
The deal fell through.

00:16:11.039 --> 00:16:12.100
They won't agree to it.

00:16:12.720 --> 00:16:13.799
My dad said

00:16:13.980 --> 00:16:16.059
Your family's asking for too much.

00:16:16.360 --> 00:16:18.179
He, he can't come up with it.

00:16:18.720 --> 00:16:20.700
And he took my ID card too.

00:16:21.559 --> 00:16:24.539
So I can't go register the marriage with you.

00:16:28.080 --> 00:16:29.279
Did you save any money from working?

00:16:31.840 --> 00:16:33.039
As long as we're of one mind,

00:16:33.360 --> 00:16:34.399
We can still work this out.

00:16:34.860 --> 00:16:35.600
I saved thirty thousand.

00:16:35.620 --> 00:16:36.399
How much did you save?

00:16:40.980 --> 00:16:42.279
About the same.

00:16:42.759 --> 00:16:43.580
Around forty thousand.

00:16:44.820 --> 00:16:45.539
Then we'll cover

00:16:45.539 --> 00:16:46.679
The gap ourselves.

00:16:48.899 --> 00:16:49.600
Whatever you say.

00:16:49.620 --> 00:16:50.840
I'll do whatever you want.

00:16:54.039 --> 00:16:55.320
Don't lie to me again.

00:16:57.159 --> 00:16:58.059
I'll never lie to you again.

00:17:01.299 --> 00:17:02.919
Did Yang Xiaofang really say that?

00:17:03.519 --> 00:17:04.440
She's willing to put up thirty thousand.

00:17:06.319 --> 00:17:07.359
Such a wonderful bride.

00:17:07.420 --> 00:17:09.220
Shouldn't you chip in a bit more?

00:17:11.220 --> 00:17:13.380
She saved thirty thousand in three years.

00:17:13.579 --> 00:17:15.339
Your future together will be great.

00:17:19.779 --> 00:17:21.460
My son is so handsome!

00:17:22.119 --> 00:17:24.059
That's why they say grown girls can't be controlled.

00:17:24.359 --> 00:17:26.119
The Yang family kept trying

00:17:26.319 --> 00:17:28.759
To squeeze money out of our family.

00:17:29.200 --> 00:17:30.440
Who knew this girl

00:17:30.700 --> 00:17:32.200
Would end up siding with outsiders.

00:17:32.460 --> 00:17:33.619
Xiaofang puts up thirty thousand,

00:17:33.779 --> 00:17:35.039
Her family drops it a bit more,

00:17:35.279 --> 00:17:35.980
And we're about there.

00:17:37.839 --> 00:17:39.359
What do you mean, "about there"?

00:17:39.819 --> 00:17:40.859
Her family wants two hundred thousand, right?

00:17:41.339 --> 00:17:42.519
Xiaofang puts up thirty thousand,

00:17:42.839 --> 00:17:44.759
So that leaves a hundred seventy thousand.

00:17:45.140 --> 00:17:45.980
I'll chip in a bit more.

00:17:46.799 --> 00:17:47.559
Chip in a bit?

00:17:47.920 --> 00:17:49.200
How much are you planning to chip in?

00:17:49.740 --> 00:17:50.900
You think money grows on trees?

00:17:51.039 --> 00:17:51.880
Instead of taking care of your parents,

00:17:52.160 --> 00:17:53.039
You're throwing it away on her.

00:17:53.440 --> 00:17:54.839
Well, they lowered their price,

00:17:54.960 --> 00:17:56.079
So shouldn't we add a little?

00:17:56.079 --> 00:17:56.839
Besides, it's my money,

00:17:56.839 --> 00:17:57.700
I get to decide.

00:17:58.339 --> 00:17:59.619
You get to decide?

00:18:00.339 --> 00:18:01.279
You don't know a damn thing.

00:18:02.059 --> 00:18:03.740
Well, then what do you mean?

00:18:04.259 --> 00:18:05.839
You don't want to put up a single cent?

00:18:06.319 --> 00:18:07.079
Oh my dear son,

00:18:07.099 --> 00:18:08.299
You're finally catching on.

00:18:10.099 --> 00:18:10.839
What do you mean?

00:18:12.220 --> 00:18:12.700
Let me ask you this.

00:18:13.480 --> 00:18:14.099
Yang Xiaofang

00:18:14.980 --> 00:18:16.140
Is willing to fork over thirty thousand.

00:18:16.299 --> 00:18:17.259
What does that tell you?

00:18:17.539 --> 00:18:18.420
It means she loves me.

00:18:18.480 --> 00:18:19.500
I should treat her even better.

00:18:19.579 --> 00:18:20.339
Bullshit!

00:18:20.579 --> 00:18:22.259
It means she's more desperate than we are.

00:18:22.359 --> 00:18:23.299
Don't push it too far.

00:18:24.180 --> 00:18:24.619
Let me ask you.

00:18:25.160 --> 00:18:26.160
Your reputation,

00:18:26.740 --> 00:18:27.900
Did I ruin it for you?

00:18:28.859 --> 00:18:29.599
Do you know what people

00:18:29.880 --> 00:18:30.700
In the village say about you?

00:18:30.700 --> 00:18:31.740
My foolish son.

00:18:36.400 --> 00:18:37.339
Don't be stubborn.

00:18:37.980 --> 00:18:39.359
You've always cared about your pride.

00:18:39.700 --> 00:18:41.380
You're not like Yang Xiaofang.

00:18:41.819 --> 00:18:43.700
She doesn't care what others say.

00:18:44.180 --> 00:18:46.339
You think we can't tell you're upset?

00:18:46.619 --> 00:18:48.079
Your dad and I can see it clear as day.

00:18:48.980 --> 00:18:50.339
Let me tell you this right now.

00:18:50.880 --> 00:18:52.559
If you don't use this chance

00:18:52.980 --> 00:18:54.799
To put Yang Xiaofang in her place,

00:18:55.539 --> 00:18:56.960
And make her obey you,

00:18:57.599 --> 00:18:58.240
Who knows

00:18:58.240 --> 00:18:59.319
What stunts she'll pull later.

00:19:00.420 --> 00:19:01.240
Don't worry.

00:19:01.539 --> 00:19:02.160
Xiaofang said

00:19:02.440 --> 00:19:03.920
The bride price is just for show,

00:19:04.099 --> 00:19:05.380
Just to satisfy her aunts.

00:19:05.700 --> 00:19:06.680
After she marries in,

00:19:06.940 --> 00:19:07.700
We won't keep a single cent.

00:19:07.759 --> 00:19:08.500
We'll return it all to you.

00:19:09.759 --> 00:19:10.559
Whatever she says,

00:19:11.220 --> 00:19:12.440
You just believe it, huh?

00:19:13.019 --> 00:19:14.259
Once that money's in their pocket,

00:19:14.259 --> 00:19:15.740
You think they'll cough it back up?

00:19:16.039 --> 00:19:16.980
Unbelievable.

00:19:17.339 --> 00:19:18.420
We're not making it hard for her.

00:19:18.599 --> 00:19:19.759
Just putting some pressure on her,

00:19:20.099 --> 00:19:21.220
So she knows to settle down with you

00:19:21.220 --> 00:19:22.259
And live a proper life.

00:19:22.980 --> 00:19:23.480
This is called

00:19:24.240 --> 00:19:25.480
Keep her on a tight leash,

00:19:25.819 --> 00:19:27.599
She's not going anywhere.

00:19:29.339 --> 00:19:30.640
Borrow money from me?

00:19:32.039 --> 00:19:34.059
Why should I lend you any money?

00:19:34.200 --> 00:19:35.220
You gave me three days.

00:19:35.599 --> 00:19:36.559
Yang Fanyan wants that much money.

00:19:36.599 --> 00:19:37.599
How am I supposed to scrape it together?

00:19:38.099 --> 00:19:38.819
I'm starting to suspect

00:19:38.880 --> 00:19:40.160
You two old flames are in cahoots,

00:19:40.240 --> 00:19:41.200
Ganging up to swindle me.

00:19:42.200 --> 00:19:43.359
Watch it, or I'll sue you for slander.

00:19:43.579 --> 00:19:44.019
Fine, go ahead and sue.

00:19:44.380 --> 00:19:44.980
Sue me.

00:19:45.240 --> 00:19:46.059
Either way, I've got no money.

00:19:46.259 --> 00:19:47.000
But if I go down,

00:19:47.140 --> 00:19:48.640
The Yang family won't get off easy.

00:19:49.359 --> 00:19:50.019
That's how it is.

00:19:50.019 --> 00:19:51.119
If this blows up,

00:19:51.359 --> 00:19:52.720
I'd worry about your official position.

00:19:53.559 --> 00:19:54.859
You're threatening me now?

00:19:55.440 --> 00:19:57.380
I wouldn't dare threaten you.

00:19:57.619 --> 00:19:58.700
But put your hand on your heart and think.

00:19:58.859 --> 00:20:01.019
Who can cough up that much cash all at once?

00:20:01.259 --> 00:20:02.160
You big shot director,

00:20:02.619 --> 00:20:03.380
Just opening your big mouth,

00:20:03.579 --> 00:20:04.339
Saying "solve it in three days."

00:20:04.640 --> 00:20:06.079
If I don't borrow, what am I supposed to do?

00:20:07.019 --> 00:20:07.500
Qi Deyao,

00:20:07.759 --> 00:20:09.160
You're always hustling this,

00:20:09.339 --> 00:20:10.299
Hustling that,

00:20:10.680 --> 00:20:11.759
And you can't scrape it together?

00:20:12.059 --> 00:20:14.000
Every family has its own troubles.

00:20:14.440 --> 00:20:15.480
If you don't mind hearing it,

00:20:15.640 --> 00:20:17.019
I'll fill you in properly.

00:20:17.200 --> 00:20:18.480
Look, this spring at our house...

00:20:18.599 --> 00:20:19.279
All right, all right, all right.

00:20:19.380 --> 00:20:19.940
Stop already.

00:20:20.640 --> 00:20:21.880
This color really suits me.

00:20:21.980 --> 00:20:22.660
Yeah.

00:20:22.759 --> 00:20:23.339
Makes your skin look fair.

00:20:24.839 --> 00:20:25.859
I think

00:20:26.240 --> 00:20:27.500
The kids' matter

00:20:27.759 --> 00:20:28.940
Shouldn't be dragged out because of me.

00:20:29.299 --> 00:20:31.000
Xiaofang's belly is already so big.

00:20:31.259 --> 00:20:31.980
Their wedding

00:20:32.059 --> 00:20:34.220
Needs to happen as soon as possible.

00:20:34.500 --> 00:20:35.160
Right.

00:20:35.640 --> 00:20:36.480
You've got a point there.

00:20:39.099 --> 00:20:39.720
But you know...

00:20:39.859 --> 00:20:40.920
All these years,

00:20:41.440 --> 00:20:43.619
I've spent all my money on the kids.

00:20:44.599 --> 00:20:45.980
I can't come up with that much.

00:20:46.519 --> 00:20:47.119
Director,

00:20:48.000 --> 00:20:49.200
Could you lend me some money?

00:20:51.220 --> 00:20:51.960
Go on, get out!

00:20:53.059 --> 00:20:54.359
My dear,

00:20:55.259 --> 00:20:56.640
What are you doing?

00:20:56.680 --> 00:20:57.920
It's just to tide me over.

00:20:58.440 --> 00:20:58.859
Later,

00:20:59.779 --> 00:21:00.980
I'll sell this bracelet

00:21:01.000 --> 00:21:01.420
And gold ring,

00:21:01.619 --> 00:21:02.359
Sell them off,

00:21:02.519 --> 00:21:03.480
And pay you back.

00:21:03.799 --> 00:21:05.500
Don't worry, just to tide me over.

00:21:06.099 --> 00:21:06.720
After the holiday,

00:21:07.480 --> 00:21:08.559
I'll sell the car and pay you back.

00:21:11.099 --> 00:21:11.980
Oh, and I brought you

00:21:12.819 --> 00:21:13.819
A Mid-Autumn gift.

00:21:14.039 --> 00:21:14.740
No, this...

00:21:15.640 --> 00:21:16.240
Hold still.

00:21:17.279 --> 00:21:19.019
Real leather, so classy.

00:21:19.700 --> 00:21:20.880
A women's director's style

00:21:20.880 --> 00:21:22.259
Is really something else.

00:21:23.880 --> 00:21:24.640
Such elegance!

00:21:24.839 --> 00:21:25.680
It makes you look even classier.

00:21:25.940 --> 00:21:27.000
Doesn't show your age at all.

00:21:27.279 --> 00:21:28.220
Can you feel it yourself?

00:21:28.700 --> 00:21:30.019
And your features are so gorgeous.

00:21:30.200 --> 00:21:31.480
It's a shame you're not an actress.

00:21:32.640 --> 00:21:33.839
I've already written the IOU.

00:21:34.359 --> 00:21:35.700
Wow, you really came

00:21:35.759 --> 00:21:36.720
Fully prepared, huh?

00:21:36.720 --> 00:21:38.480
Of course, business is business.

00:21:38.740 --> 00:21:39.759
Well, let me take a look then.

00:21:40.259 --> 00:21:41.079
How much do you want to borrow?

00:21:41.900 --> 00:21:42.680
Please have a look.

00:21:48.960 --> 00:21:49.500
Mom.

00:21:50.079 --> 00:21:51.220
What's for lunch?

00:21:51.740 --> 00:21:52.140
You...

00:21:53.259 --> 00:21:55.140
Weren't you going to Dongbao's?

00:21:55.880 --> 00:21:56.759
Why are you still home?

00:21:57.720 --> 00:21:58.799
He stood me up.

00:21:58.920 --> 00:21:59.720
Who's here?

00:21:59.720 --> 00:22:00.579
We have guests?

00:22:01.160 --> 00:22:02.440
It's, you know...

00:22:02.480 --> 00:22:03.539
It's all handled, Qiu Mei.

00:22:03.960 --> 00:22:04.640
All handled.

00:22:07.299 --> 00:22:09.339
Wait, didn't you go out?

00:22:10.119 --> 00:22:11.119
Hey, what are you hiding?

00:22:11.279 --> 00:22:12.039
Nothing.

00:22:12.039 --> 00:22:12.700
Let me see it.

00:22:12.940 --> 00:22:14.539
What are you up to behind my back? Show me.

00:22:14.720 --> 00:22:15.519
Fine, fine, fine.

00:22:16.019 --> 00:22:16.559
Take a look.

00:22:17.359 --> 00:22:18.720
It's for your own good.

00:22:19.119 --> 00:22:20.319
We're helping you borrow money.

00:22:20.539 --> 00:22:21.420
To save face, you know.

00:22:23.660 --> 00:22:25.680
Why did you use my name to borrow money?

00:22:25.980 --> 00:22:27.059
If I needed to borrow, I'd do it myself.

00:22:27.559 --> 00:22:28.660
Who am I doing this for?

00:22:29.079 --> 00:22:30.359
You really think on your own,

00:22:30.359 --> 00:22:31.759
You could borrow this much money?

00:22:32.259 --> 00:22:33.920
Without so much as a word,

00:22:33.960 --> 00:22:34.880
You let Yang Xiaofang

00:22:35.519 --> 00:22:37.160
End up pregnant with your kid,

00:22:37.700 --> 00:22:38.759
Come back demanding a wedding,

00:22:39.839 --> 00:22:41.279
Asking for this much money right off the bat!

00:22:42.740 --> 00:22:43.900
Even if you smashed

00:22:43.900 --> 00:22:44.579
Every bone in my body

00:22:44.619 --> 00:22:45.740
And sold them, it wouldn't be worth this much!

00:22:45.920 --> 00:22:46.900
So who's screwing over who here?

00:22:47.519 --> 00:22:48.819
Uh, Second Uncle,

00:22:48.900 --> 00:22:50.160
Take it easy with the drinks.

00:22:50.240 --> 00:22:51.140
More food's coming.

00:22:51.720 --> 00:22:52.779
Sure, sure, sure.

00:22:55.140 --> 00:22:55.720
Son.

00:22:56.819 --> 00:22:57.720
You want to get married,

00:22:57.900 --> 00:22:59.140
But our family really has no money.

00:22:59.339 --> 00:23:00.420
We had no choice but to borrow.

00:23:01.500 --> 00:23:02.200
Let me tell you,

00:23:02.960 --> 00:23:04.000
None of our relatives

00:23:04.539 --> 00:23:05.900
Were willing to lend a cent.

00:23:06.400 --> 00:23:07.759
I talked my mouth dry,

00:23:07.839 --> 00:23:09.660
Appealing to reason and emotion.

00:23:09.980 --> 00:23:11.500
I had to guilt-trip them with family ties.

00:23:12.000 --> 00:23:12.740
You go right now,

00:23:13.000 --> 00:23:13.779
Take back the IOUs,

00:23:13.819 --> 00:23:14.619
And return their money.

00:23:15.779 --> 00:23:16.559
I want to see

00:23:17.079 --> 00:23:17.740
If Yang Xiaofang

00:23:18.920 --> 00:23:19.640
Still marries you

00:23:19.980 --> 00:23:20.960
Once she knows you're broke.

00:23:21.740 --> 00:23:22.279
Fine, I'll return it.

00:23:22.519 --> 00:23:23.720
Xiaofang doesn't care about money.

00:23:24.799 --> 00:23:25.200
Son...

00:23:25.579 --> 00:23:26.180
Xiaofang

00:23:26.680 --> 00:23:27.259
May not care,

00:23:27.559 --> 00:23:29.319
But the Yang family sure does.

00:23:29.960 --> 00:23:30.759
Qi Xiaowei,

00:23:31.160 --> 00:23:32.220
You'd better think this through.

00:23:32.640 --> 00:23:33.619
Everything I could do to help you,

00:23:33.640 --> 00:23:34.859
I've already done.

00:23:35.539 --> 00:23:36.359
If you return the money

00:23:36.480 --> 00:23:37.420
And can't get married later,

00:23:37.579 --> 00:23:38.720
That's your own problem.

00:23:39.339 --> 00:23:40.740
No one's going to bail you out anymore.

00:23:41.339 --> 00:23:42.759
Can't earn a single cent all day,

00:23:42.759 --> 00:23:44.400
But still want to save face, huh?

00:23:45.460 --> 00:23:46.839
Fine, they're all sitting right there.

00:23:47.319 --> 00:23:48.240
If you've got any backbone,

00:23:48.440 --> 00:23:48.880
Go.

00:23:49.339 --> 00:23:50.059
Go return it right now.

00:23:50.400 --> 00:23:50.740
Go on.

00:23:51.440 --> 00:23:52.000
You go.

00:23:55.900 --> 00:23:56.460
Xiaowei's here!

00:23:57.240 --> 00:23:57.900
Xiaowei's here!

00:23:57.900 --> 00:23:58.920
Come on, come on, Xiaowei's here.

00:23:58.920 --> 00:24:00.759
We were waiting. Come, come have a drink.

00:24:04.859 --> 00:24:05.640
Xiaofang.

00:24:09.519 --> 00:24:10.279
Xiaofang.

00:24:10.799 --> 00:24:11.559
Coming.

00:24:12.960 --> 00:24:13.720
Xiaofang.

00:24:15.720 --> 00:24:17.200
How much have you had to drink?

00:24:17.519 --> 00:24:18.420
You can't even stand straight.

00:24:18.460 --> 00:24:19.000
Sit down right now.

00:24:19.220 --> 00:24:19.980
Is everything right?

00:24:19.980 --> 00:24:20.380
Sit.

00:24:21.599 --> 00:24:22.259
Xiaofang.

00:24:28.420 --> 00:24:29.720
I love it when you boss me around

00:24:30.720 --> 00:24:32.140
Boss me around good, boss me around great

00:24:32.319 --> 00:24:33.339
Boss me around

00:24:35.140 --> 00:24:36.160
Like a champ.

00:24:38.700 --> 00:24:39.779
How much did you drink?

00:24:44.140 --> 00:24:45.559
My wife is the best

00:24:48.759 --> 00:24:51.000
Everyone else treats me like a fool

00:24:52.299 --> 00:24:53.500
Only my wife, right now

00:24:53.539 --> 00:24:55.140
Still puts up with my nonsense

00:24:57.880 --> 00:24:59.259
The money issue is handled

00:25:04.059 --> 00:25:04.779
It's done

00:25:07.279 --> 00:25:08.240
Where did the money come from?

00:25:09.880 --> 00:25:10.839
That's not important

00:25:12.200 --> 00:25:13.400
What matters most

00:25:19.359 --> 00:25:20.819
Is that I, Qi Xiaowei

00:25:21.160 --> 00:25:22.839
Have finally gotten everything

00:25:22.859 --> 00:25:24.160
Completely sorted out

00:25:26.079 --> 00:25:27.819
Now I can rightfully

00:25:27.859 --> 00:25:30.240
Call Yang Xiaofang my wife

00:25:31.279 --> 00:25:32.539
What else can they yap about?

00:25:33.660 --> 00:25:35.140
We're protected by the law

00:25:35.180 --> 00:25:36.460
Okay, don't get carried away, put me down

00:25:39.619 --> 00:25:40.880
Your dad really agreed?

00:25:41.700 --> 00:25:43.380
This whole thing is now

00:25:44.259 --> 00:25:45.380
A done deal

00:25:47.579 --> 00:25:48.259
Xiaofang

00:25:50.359 --> 00:25:51.480
I, Qi Xiaowei,

00:25:51.920 --> 00:25:53.420
Will treat you and the baby

00:25:54.099 --> 00:25:55.359
Like precious treasures

00:25:55.460 --> 00:25:56.240
I'll be good to you both

00:25:56.759 --> 00:25:57.880
Xiaofang, you gotta believe me

00:25:57.960 --> 00:25:58.480
Okay?

00:25:58.579 --> 00:26:00.180
Believe me, come on, believe me

00:26:04.319 --> 00:26:05.680
Qi Xiaowei, look at me

00:26:05.960 --> 00:26:06.619
Don't go crazy on me

00:26:06.819 --> 00:26:07.380
Stand up straight

00:26:09.119 --> 00:26:10.500
Don't hide anything from me

00:26:12.119 --> 00:26:13.420
Tell me whatever's going on

00:26:16.119 --> 00:26:17.240
As long as we're on the same page

00:26:17.240 --> 00:26:18.519
We can solve anything

00:26:18.559 --> 00:26:19.079
Right?

00:26:24.220 --> 00:26:26.599
It's all already solved

00:26:27.200 --> 00:26:27.880
Xiaofang

00:26:28.440 --> 00:26:29.500
Come on, come on

00:26:29.519 --> 00:26:30.119
Xiaowei's here

00:26:30.119 --> 00:26:31.240
Come on, Xiaowei, over here

00:26:31.259 --> 00:26:32.700
Hurry up and sit down, sit sit

00:26:33.900 --> 00:26:34.619
We've been waiting forever

00:26:35.240 --> 00:26:35.960
Just waiting for you

00:26:36.799 --> 00:26:37.299
Look at you

00:26:37.759 --> 00:26:38.759
Back from the big city

00:26:38.920 --> 00:26:39.680
You're really different now

00:26:39.839 --> 00:26:41.420
Winning at love and career

00:26:41.579 --> 00:26:42.700
If you need anything, just say it

00:26:43.420 --> 00:26:44.940
We're family, no need to be formal

00:26:45.279 --> 00:26:45.819
Yeah, yeah, yeah

00:26:45.819 --> 00:26:46.940
We're all family, don't hold back

00:26:47.799 --> 00:26:48.700
If there's trouble, just say so

00:26:48.799 --> 00:26:49.680
Don't be shy at all

00:26:49.700 --> 00:26:50.259
Xiaowei

00:26:50.720 --> 00:26:51.960
Didn't you have something to say?

00:26:52.339 --> 00:26:52.720
Go ahead

00:26:53.019 --> 00:26:53.640
Speak your mind

00:26:59.579 --> 00:27:00.319
I...

00:27:01.980 --> 00:27:02.839
I...

00:27:05.279 --> 00:27:05.960
Have no trouble

00:27:06.319 --> 00:27:07.119
No trouble at all

00:27:07.720 --> 00:27:08.359
No trouble

00:27:08.660 --> 00:27:09.339
No trouble

00:27:09.599 --> 00:27:11.000
Whatever's up, just tell us

00:27:19.599 --> 00:27:20.859
Go home and drink plenty of water

00:27:22.420 --> 00:27:22.940
Off you go

00:27:23.980 --> 00:27:24.440
I'm leaving

00:27:32.099 --> 00:27:34.279
Never thought my name, Qi Xiaowei,

00:27:34.299 --> 00:27:35.140
Would be worth so much

00:28:02.059 --> 00:28:03.000
Why are there so many people here?

00:28:03.759 --> 00:28:04.660
They're all waiting for you.

00:28:09.059 --> 00:28:09.460
Fanyan.

00:28:09.900 --> 00:28:11.299
This is between our two families.

00:28:11.819 --> 00:28:12.700
Why bring so many people?

00:28:12.700 --> 00:28:13.440
What's the meaning of this?

00:28:13.680 --> 00:28:15.720
It was between our two families,

00:28:16.299 --> 00:28:17.440
But I couldn't stop you

00:28:17.579 --> 00:28:18.940
From running around all day

00:28:19.200 --> 00:28:20.539
Borrowing money everywhere.

00:28:21.019 --> 00:28:22.200
Look at everyone standing here.

00:28:22.539 --> 00:28:24.279
Didn't they all lend you money?

00:28:24.940 --> 00:28:26.299
If people didn't know better,

00:28:26.559 --> 00:28:27.839
They'd think the Yang family

00:28:27.940 --> 00:28:29.039
Was marrying off a daughter

00:28:29.460 --> 00:28:30.759
Just to drive the Qi family

00:28:30.759 --> 00:28:31.799
Into the ground.

00:28:32.539 --> 00:28:33.079
Fanyan,

00:28:34.319 --> 00:28:36.440
Our family absolutely doesn't mean that.

00:28:36.700 --> 00:28:37.339
You're overthinking.

00:28:39.279 --> 00:28:39.920
Our family

00:28:39.980 --> 00:28:41.119
Really doesn't have that much money.

00:28:41.480 --> 00:28:42.240
That's why I've been

00:28:42.400 --> 00:28:44.200
Begging and borrowing all over.

00:28:44.319 --> 00:28:45.440
Even broke, even in debt,

00:28:45.680 --> 00:28:47.299
We're still bringing Xiaofang into the family.

00:28:47.799 --> 00:28:48.140
So,

00:28:48.200 --> 00:28:49.440
The Qi family has done

00:28:49.700 --> 00:28:50.940
Everything humanly possible, right?

00:28:50.980 --> 00:28:51.440
Right?

00:28:52.819 --> 00:28:54.180
Old Qi borrowed money

00:28:54.579 --> 00:28:56.180
Just to tide things over.

00:28:56.559 --> 00:28:57.940
We're all neighbors here,

00:28:58.119 --> 00:28:59.819
And we'd love to see these two young folks

00:28:59.900 --> 00:29:00.940
Get married as soon as possible.

00:29:01.700 --> 00:29:02.880
Everyone's willing to help out.

00:29:02.920 --> 00:29:03.539
Right?

00:29:03.660 --> 00:29:04.819
We're all happy to help.

00:29:05.119 --> 00:29:06.079
Old Miao's right.

00:29:06.700 --> 00:29:07.980
We're all glad to lend a hand.

00:29:08.920 --> 00:29:09.420
Fanyan,

00:29:09.779 --> 00:29:10.759
These are all small matters.

00:29:11.299 --> 00:29:12.140
What matters most right now

00:29:12.200 --> 00:29:14.220
Is getting Xiaofang married quickly.

00:29:14.460 --> 00:29:15.059
That's what really counts.

00:29:15.059 --> 00:29:15.740
Yes, yes, yes.

00:29:15.859 --> 00:29:16.440
So touching.

00:29:17.160 --> 00:29:18.619
Deeply moved.

00:29:19.819 --> 00:29:20.700
I, Qi Deyao,

00:29:21.539 --> 00:29:22.539
Sincerely stand here

00:29:22.640 --> 00:29:23.579
To thank you all.

00:29:24.500 --> 00:29:25.299
Thank you, thank you.

00:29:25.799 --> 00:29:27.440
After the kids' wedding is over,

00:29:27.740 --> 00:29:28.940
I'll take everything valuable at home,

00:29:29.079 --> 00:29:29.680
Bring it all out,

00:29:29.940 --> 00:29:30.460
And sell it off.

00:29:30.779 --> 00:29:31.420
Once I've got the money,

00:29:31.720 --> 00:29:32.680
I'll pay everyone back.

00:29:33.059 --> 00:29:34.799
Alright, no rush, Old Qi.

00:29:35.039 --> 00:29:35.779
The money,

00:29:36.759 --> 00:29:37.779
Who's paying it back?

00:29:38.799 --> 00:29:40.319
Whoever borrowed it pays it back, of course.

00:29:40.400 --> 00:29:41.960
Yeah, right.

00:29:42.400 --> 00:29:43.339
Qi Deyao,

00:29:43.700 --> 00:29:44.460
This money,

00:29:45.359 --> 00:29:45.940
Are you paying it back?

00:29:46.299 --> 00:29:47.420
Of course I am.

00:29:47.700 --> 00:29:49.140
The Qi family still has

00:29:49.480 --> 00:29:50.519
Some dignity to uphold.

00:29:51.519 --> 00:29:52.359
Qi Deyao,

00:29:53.200 --> 00:29:54.779
So you do care about face sometimes.

00:29:55.059 --> 00:29:55.599
Unbelievable.

00:29:57.000 --> 00:29:58.420
Let me give everyone a heads-up.

00:29:58.859 --> 00:29:59.819
Take out those IOUs quickly

00:29:59.880 --> 00:30:00.799
And take a look.

00:30:01.059 --> 00:30:02.099
Isn't the name written on them

00:30:02.180 --> 00:30:04.059
Qi Xiaowei's?

00:30:07.000 --> 00:30:07.759
Old Qi said

00:30:07.839 --> 00:30:08.740
We're all family anyway

00:30:08.759 --> 00:30:09.680
So it doesn't matter who pays it back

00:30:09.960 --> 00:30:11.259
That's what he told me back then, too

00:30:11.500 --> 00:30:12.339
Same here

00:30:13.839 --> 00:30:14.660
Here, take a look

00:30:14.900 --> 00:30:15.859
Qi Xiaowei

00:30:17.299 --> 00:30:18.180
This old man Qi

00:30:18.339 --> 00:30:19.680
He's really got it all figured out

00:30:19.799 --> 00:30:21.319
So damn crafty

00:30:21.700 --> 00:30:23.740
He borrowed the money in his son's name

00:30:24.000 --> 00:30:24.640
So paying it back

00:30:25.279 --> 00:30:26.759
Has to be on the son too

00:30:27.420 --> 00:30:28.900
So if Xiaofang and Xiaowei

00:30:28.980 --> 00:30:29.640
Get married

00:30:29.799 --> 00:30:32.559
Then it becomes a debt Qi Xiaowei and Xiaofang

00:30:32.680 --> 00:30:34.559
Racked up for their wedding

00:30:34.819 --> 00:30:35.660
And by then, this debt

00:30:35.700 --> 00:30:36.980
Qi Xiaowei and Xiaofang

00:30:37.160 --> 00:30:38.140
Will have to pay together

00:30:38.339 --> 00:30:38.900
Right?

00:30:39.539 --> 00:30:40.299
Qi Deyao

00:30:40.640 --> 00:30:41.799
Your Qi Xiaowei

00:30:41.799 --> 00:30:43.579
Doesn't even have a proper job

00:30:43.839 --> 00:30:45.559
No way he'll ever pay it back

00:30:46.039 --> 00:30:46.819
Old Qi

00:30:47.519 --> 00:30:48.380
When you borrowed the money

00:30:48.400 --> 00:30:50.000
You talked it up like anything

00:30:50.359 --> 00:30:52.180
Turns out this was your little scheme

00:30:52.180 --> 00:30:53.019
That's right

00:30:53.140 --> 00:30:53.759
Xiaofang is not going to

00:30:53.759 --> 00:30:54.859
Pay back this money for them

00:30:55.160 --> 00:30:56.039
You've been had!

00:30:56.059 --> 00:30:57.000
Go ask him for the money

00:30:57.039 --> 00:30:58.500
No, Qiu Mei, give me my money back!

00:31:02.859 --> 00:31:03.460
Director Miao

00:31:04.420 --> 00:31:05.759
If he keeps making trouble like this

00:31:06.279 --> 00:31:06.839
Three days

00:31:07.599 --> 00:31:08.380
We'll never come to terms

00:31:14.460 --> 00:31:16.140
He's got osteoporosis

00:31:17.359 --> 00:31:18.160
He's faking an injury!

00:31:18.420 --> 00:31:19.160
Old Qi

00:31:21.220 --> 00:31:22.640
Qi Deyao, Qi Deyao

00:31:23.000 --> 00:31:24.940
How can you be so shameless?

00:31:25.299 --> 00:31:26.420
How am I shameless?

00:31:27.380 --> 00:31:28.119
It's obviously

00:31:28.599 --> 00:31:29.380
A losing deal

00:31:29.839 --> 00:31:30.779
Only a fool would take it

00:31:32.019 --> 00:31:33.759
You're just obsessed with money

00:31:34.400 --> 00:31:35.920
You think I want to be?

00:31:36.299 --> 00:31:37.779
Look at what the Yang family's asking for

00:31:38.660 --> 00:31:40.039
If I weren't obsessed with money

00:31:40.380 --> 00:31:41.900
Marrying off my two sons

00:31:42.240 --> 00:31:43.599
Would be the death of me

00:31:44.339 --> 00:31:45.559
Let me lay it out right here

00:31:45.759 --> 00:31:46.440
Tomorrow

00:31:46.779 --> 00:31:47.819
The matter between your two families

00:31:48.400 --> 00:31:49.859
Must be settled

00:31:50.440 --> 00:31:50.900
Fine

00:31:52.859 --> 00:31:53.759
Then I'll go home and hang myself

00:31:54.279 --> 00:31:54.960
I've got no money

00:31:55.480 --> 00:31:56.400
But I've got one life to give

00:31:59.140 --> 00:31:59.839
Fine, fine, fine

00:32:04.700 --> 00:32:06.039
If it weren't for Fanyan's situation

00:32:06.920 --> 00:32:08.259
I wouldn't bother getting involved

00:32:19.660 --> 00:32:20.680
Old Qi

00:32:22.740 --> 00:32:23.700
Let me tell you

00:32:25.579 --> 00:32:27.740
Xiaofang marrying into your family

00:32:28.440 --> 00:32:29.940
Means you only gain, never lose

00:32:30.660 --> 00:32:31.900
You're the God of Wealth!

00:32:32.180 --> 00:32:33.420
You say no loss, so no loss?

00:32:34.759 --> 00:32:35.500
Let me tell you

00:32:47.259 --> 00:32:48.599
You can still laugh?

00:32:49.079 --> 00:32:51.059
The whole village is laughing at you.

00:32:57.119 --> 00:32:57.880
Demolition.

00:32:58.859 --> 00:32:59.940
It's really being demolished?

00:33:00.319 --> 00:33:01.660
It was just a few days ago

00:33:01.779 --> 00:33:03.019
That I heard about it in the county.

00:33:03.700 --> 00:33:04.880
They're building a huge

00:33:04.920 --> 00:33:06.599
Theme park in our area.

00:33:07.160 --> 00:33:07.940
And our village

00:33:08.259 --> 00:33:09.920
Is within the demolition zone.

00:33:10.640 --> 00:33:12.119
Compensation is per person.

00:33:12.539 --> 00:33:13.579
Once Xiaofang joins your family,

00:33:14.279 --> 00:33:15.319
With the baby in her belly,

00:33:15.680 --> 00:33:18.059
Your family gains two more heads.

00:33:18.480 --> 00:33:18.960
Have you done

00:33:19.559 --> 00:33:20.220
The math on this?

00:33:20.819 --> 00:33:22.140
You'd only stand to gain.

00:33:23.859 --> 00:33:24.400
Right, right, right.

00:33:24.859 --> 00:33:25.319
Exactly.

00:33:26.640 --> 00:33:27.579
This deal's worth doing.

00:33:30.880 --> 00:33:32.279
And what math are you doing?

00:33:33.799 --> 00:33:34.500
What math?

00:33:35.220 --> 00:33:36.359
The getting-rich math.

00:33:38.259 --> 00:33:39.420
With or without the rooster crowing,

00:33:39.700 --> 00:33:41.160
Dawn breaks all the same.

00:33:41.720 --> 00:33:42.740
So I'm the one getting rich?

00:33:44.480 --> 00:33:45.460
Xiaofang,

00:33:45.920 --> 00:33:47.079
We've got to marry her.

00:33:49.900 --> 00:33:51.180
What did old Miao tell you?

00:33:51.759 --> 00:33:53.259
Why the sudden change of heart?

00:33:58.779 --> 00:34:00.079
How could I tell you?

00:34:00.299 --> 00:34:00.839
Once you know,

00:34:00.920 --> 00:34:01.940
The whole village knows.

00:34:05.539 --> 00:34:06.539
So you used my name

00:34:06.660 --> 00:34:07.880
To sign that IOU

00:34:07.900 --> 00:34:08.820
Because you wanted me

00:34:08.820 --> 00:34:10.179
To pay it back together with Xiaofang.

00:34:10.239 --> 00:34:11.900
Only a fool would believe you.

00:34:14.960 --> 00:34:15.860
Son, don't get worked up.

00:34:16.079 --> 00:34:17.000
That money,

00:34:17.000 --> 00:34:18.059
We gave it right back on the spot.

00:34:18.119 --> 00:34:19.179
What's the use of giving it back?

00:34:19.539 --> 00:34:20.659
Will their family agree

00:34:20.780 --> 00:34:21.880
To let me marry Xiaofang?

00:34:36.320 --> 00:34:36.699
Take it.

00:34:37.099 --> 00:34:38.000
Go marry Xiaofang home

00:34:38.480 --> 00:34:39.699
In grand style for me.

00:34:44.260 --> 00:34:44.659
Look,

00:34:45.539 --> 00:34:46.900
The good news came too suddenly.

00:34:47.679 --> 00:34:48.619
My son's stunned speechless.

00:34:51.460 --> 00:34:52.219
You had money

00:34:52.800 --> 00:34:53.260
And lied to me.

00:34:54.480 --> 00:34:56.380
Wouldn't give it to me, made me borrow.

00:34:57.559 --> 00:34:58.500
Is toying with me fun?

00:34:58.739 --> 00:35:00.000
Son, we're not toying with you.

00:35:00.079 --> 00:35:01.000
Our family really couldn't

00:35:01.019 --> 00:35:02.380
Come up with this much money at once.

00:35:02.820 --> 00:35:03.460
It's just that you're

00:35:03.500 --> 00:35:04.460
So dead-set on marrying Xiaofang.

00:35:04.539 --> 00:35:05.360
You'd marry her come hell or high water,

00:35:05.380 --> 00:35:06.360
And you love her so much,

00:35:06.800 --> 00:35:08.500
So I dug into my coffin savings.

00:35:09.079 --> 00:35:10.559
Your dad's got your back, doesn't he?

00:35:10.800 --> 00:35:11.320
Xiaowei,

00:35:12.320 --> 00:35:12.940
Listen,

00:35:13.079 --> 00:35:14.900
Your dad's coughed up all this money.

00:35:15.619 --> 00:35:16.900
Go and talk it over with Xiaofang.

00:35:18.179 --> 00:35:18.860
You said you'd drag it out.

00:35:19.460 --> 00:35:20.480
You're the one who wouldn't give me money.

00:35:21.360 --> 00:35:22.039
And now,

00:35:22.039 --> 00:35:23.659
You're the one telling me to marry her.

00:35:24.219 --> 00:35:25.219
Not even letting me keep my hair.

00:35:25.579 --> 00:35:26.159
Whatever I do,

00:35:26.199 --> 00:35:27.420
I've got to follow your orders.

00:35:28.380 --> 00:35:29.940
When I die someday,

00:35:30.119 --> 00:35:31.659
Which urn my ashes go into,

00:35:31.820 --> 00:35:32.780
I've got to listen to you too?

00:35:32.840 --> 00:35:34.340
Let me ask you, is that right?

00:35:50.179 --> 00:35:50.760
No need to ask.

00:35:51.820 --> 00:35:52.920
When you die, same as me,

00:35:52.980 --> 00:35:54.059
You'll rest in the family tomb.

00:35:55.019 --> 00:35:56.199
As for your child,

00:35:57.119 --> 00:35:59.239
That depends on who Xiaofang marries.

00:36:50.280 --> 00:36:50.780
Xiaofang.

00:36:51.340 --> 00:36:51.800
Xiaofang.

00:36:55.280 --> 00:36:55.719
Here.

00:36:56.380 --> 00:36:56.860
Take it.

00:36:57.579 --> 00:36:58.219
About the money,

00:36:58.800 --> 00:36:59.739
I sorted it out with my dad.

00:37:06.820 --> 00:37:07.480
Qi Xiaowei.

00:37:09.039 --> 00:37:10.659
If your name's so valuable,

00:37:11.199 --> 00:37:12.219
Why'd you use your dad's bank card

00:37:12.280 --> 00:37:13.079
In the first place?

00:37:15.960 --> 00:37:17.039
What are you talking about?

00:37:20.039 --> 00:37:20.639
Your family borrowed money

00:37:20.639 --> 00:37:21.780
Under your name.

00:37:22.599 --> 00:37:23.639
You knew all along,

00:37:23.659 --> 00:37:24.119
Didn't you?

00:37:28.480 --> 00:37:29.719
You know how my dad is.

00:37:31.500 --> 00:37:31.940
He...

00:37:32.380 --> 00:37:33.599
He forged my signature.

00:37:35.139 --> 00:37:36.559
But this time I stood my ground.

00:37:37.199 --> 00:37:38.300
I had a huge fight with him.

00:37:38.500 --> 00:37:39.780
And I got the money back, didn't I?

00:37:43.280 --> 00:37:43.619
Fang.

00:37:43.719 --> 00:37:45.300
Let's just put this behind us,

00:37:45.300 --> 00:37:45.760
Okay?

00:37:51.280 --> 00:37:51.960
Qi Xiaowei.

00:37:53.320 --> 00:37:54.059
Didn't I tell you

00:37:54.099 --> 00:37:55.059
Not to lie to me?

00:38:06.880 --> 00:38:07.420
Yes.

00:38:08.280 --> 00:38:08.940
Yes, I...

00:38:10.260 --> 00:38:11.019
I know what I did

00:38:11.739 --> 00:38:13.159
Was wrong.

00:38:14.079 --> 00:38:15.340
But you have to think about me too,

00:38:15.340 --> 00:38:16.039
Right?

00:38:17.239 --> 00:38:18.920
Who am I doing this for?

00:38:19.420 --> 00:38:20.539
It's for the two of us,

00:38:21.019 --> 00:38:21.860
For our family.

00:38:22.320 --> 00:38:23.780
Once the baby is born,

00:38:23.980 --> 00:38:25.159
We'll need a lot of money.

00:38:25.719 --> 00:38:26.880
Only with money in hand

00:38:26.980 --> 00:38:28.320
Can we feel secure, right?

00:38:30.400 --> 00:38:31.199
Listen, Xiaofang.

00:38:32.960 --> 00:38:33.760
I've got it all figured out.

00:38:34.199 --> 00:38:35.639
We'll just keep this money,

00:38:36.619 --> 00:38:38.159
And not pay my dad back later.

00:38:38.679 --> 00:38:39.980
Even if he throws a fit,

00:38:40.159 --> 00:38:41.079
I'll handle it.

00:38:42.599 --> 00:38:43.519
What are you saying?

00:38:44.739 --> 00:38:45.519
Qi Xiaowei.

00:38:45.900 --> 00:38:47.559
You're lying to both sides just to get married?

00:38:49.039 --> 00:38:49.699
What are your dad and I

00:38:49.739 --> 00:38:50.960
To you, exactly?

00:38:51.840 --> 00:38:53.059
Is this really solving anything?

00:38:53.139 --> 00:38:54.460
You're just pitting me and your dad against each other.

00:39:08.280 --> 00:39:09.219
Lying to both sides?

00:39:11.219 --> 00:39:11.699
Yeah.

00:39:12.579 --> 00:39:13.480
I did lie.

00:39:15.260 --> 00:39:16.099
But is that so wrong?

00:39:17.380 --> 00:39:18.119
I'm not capable enough,

00:39:18.199 --> 00:39:19.099
So I wanted to squeeze a bit more

00:39:19.179 --> 00:39:20.460
Out of my dad. Is that wrong?

00:39:20.500 --> 00:39:21.260
I just want us

00:39:21.340 --> 00:39:21.860
To have a better life.

00:39:21.860 --> 00:39:23.239
Is that wrong, Yang Xiaofang?

00:39:29.940 --> 00:39:30.579
Can you please

00:39:30.599 --> 00:39:31.480
Change your attitude?

00:39:38.840 --> 00:39:39.699
Change what?

00:39:40.380 --> 00:39:41.280
The way you disregard others,

00:39:41.320 --> 00:39:41.900
Disregard me,

00:39:41.940 --> 00:39:43.119
Disregard my feelings.

00:39:50.239 --> 00:39:51.619
I'm begging you, open your eyes.

00:39:52.260 --> 00:39:53.199
Look around you.

00:39:53.480 --> 00:39:54.719
This isn't Shenzhen.

00:39:54.780 --> 00:39:56.360
So many eyes are watching us,

00:39:56.380 --> 00:39:56.940
Watching me.

00:39:57.019 --> 00:39:58.199
What am I supposed to do?

00:40:01.480 --> 00:40:02.440
I'll be honest with you.

00:40:03.219 --> 00:40:04.559
I never wanted to come back.

00:40:04.940 --> 00:40:06.199
I wanted to stay in Shenzhen.

00:40:06.579 --> 00:40:08.119
But you said you wanted to stay here.

00:40:08.199 --> 00:40:09.579
Fine, okay, no problem.

00:40:09.820 --> 00:40:10.980
I'll stay here with you.

00:40:11.300 --> 00:40:12.340
But I'm begging you,

00:40:12.460 --> 00:40:13.619
Please change your attitude,

00:40:13.619 --> 00:40:14.079
Okay?

00:40:14.079 --> 00:40:15.300
I don't want to be treated

00:40:15.619 --> 00:40:16.500
Like a fool anymore,

00:40:16.539 --> 00:40:17.699
With people pointing fingers

00:40:17.760 --> 00:40:18.900
And gossiping behind my back.

00:40:43.940 --> 00:40:45.300
You said before

00:40:46.440 --> 00:40:48.300
You hoped I'd never change.

00:40:56.300 --> 00:40:56.800
Yeah.

00:41:00.300 --> 00:41:01.400
That was when we were just dating.

00:41:03.920 --> 00:41:04.719
Who doesn't get carried away

00:41:04.739 --> 00:41:05.679
When they're in love?

00:41:07.400 --> 00:41:08.719
But now we're getting married.

00:41:10.400 --> 00:41:11.760
There are so many people around,

00:41:12.719 --> 00:41:14.960
So many things I have to deal with.

00:41:15.460 --> 00:41:16.920
I can't just think about you alone.

00:41:16.920 --> 00:41:17.440
Right?

00:43:24.340 --> 00:43:25.340
Xiaofang said

00:43:25.480 --> 00:43:27.619
She doesn't want Qi Xiaowei's bride price

00:43:27.760 --> 00:43:29.739
And she's not marrying him either.

00:43:30.380 --> 00:43:32.460
That Qi family is just outrageous.

00:43:32.760 --> 00:43:34.480
Xiaofang's right not to marry him.

00:43:34.900 --> 00:43:35.519
The baby,

00:43:35.780 --> 00:43:36.699
We'll raise it ourselves.

00:43:36.980 --> 00:43:38.780
Xiaofang, don't you worry.

00:43:39.000 --> 00:43:39.920
There are plenty of men out there.

00:43:40.179 --> 00:43:40.980
You can not only pick,

00:43:40.980 --> 00:43:41.760
You can take your sweet time choosing.

00:43:41.940 --> 00:43:42.380
Right.

00:43:43.659 --> 00:43:44.380
I don't agree.

00:43:45.820 --> 00:43:46.460
Yang Xiaofang,

00:43:47.239 --> 00:43:48.239
You're pregnant.

00:43:48.579 --> 00:43:49.579
If you don't marry me,

00:43:49.659 --> 00:43:50.599
Who else are you gonna find?

00:43:50.659 --> 00:43:51.539
Who would even want you?

